    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are absolutely no scratches, dents, or stone chips to be found. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery still smelling new and every electronic feature functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and meticulously maintained with a full service history available. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that needs absolutely nothing.",
