      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine. This unit features the desirable 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. Extensive preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive double-VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis is sorted with Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings for sharp handling. While the exterior shows light road-use patina, the engine pulls strong to its 8,000 RPM redline with perfect compression. A turn-key enthusiast build with exceptional mechanical bones.",
